{"type":"message","id":"82211cb7","parentId":"2e0880e2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:58:46.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a full understanding of the architecture. The code needs these things to add a new analyst:\n\n1. Create a new analyst file in `tradingagents/agents/analysts/`\n2. Add the import in `tradingagents/agents/__init__.py`\n3. Add the analyst to `_create_tool_nodes` in `tradingagents/graph/trading_graph.py`\n4. Add the analyst in `setup.py` in `tradingagents/graph/setup.py`\n5. Update `ANALYST_ORDER`, `ANALYST_AGENT_NAMES`, and `ANALYST_REPORT_MAP` in `api/main.py`\n6. Add report logging in `tradingagents/graph/trading_graph.py` `_log_state` method\n\nNow let me create the backup and development plan. First, let me backup the relevant files, then create a modified version to add more analysts.\n\nLet me understand what types of analysts would be useful to add. Looking at the existing ones:\n1. market - K线和技术指标\n2. social - 社交媒体分析 \n3. news - 新闻和内部交易\n4. fundamentals - 基本面分析\n5. macro - 宏观分析\n6. smart_money - 聪明钱分析\n7. sentiment - 情绪分析\n8. game_theory - 博弈论分析\n\nPotential new analysts:\n1. **行业分析(industry)** - 行业趋势和竞争对手分析\n2. **估值分析(valuation)** - DCF、市盈率等估值方法\n3. **财务质量(financial_quality)** - 盈利能力、现金流质量\n4. **管理层分析(management)** - 管理团队评估\n5. **风险分析(risk)** - 特定风险因素\n6. **ESG分析(esg)** - ESG评分\n7. **机构持仓分析(institutional)** - 机构持仓变化\n8. **期权分析(options)** - 期权持仓分析\n\n\n9. **资金流向(flows)** - 资金进出分析\n10. **季节性分析(seasonality)** - 历史季节性模式\n\nI'll proceed with implementing these additional analysts systematically.","thinkingSignature":"62a3d74dae968afaa81c3167bddb8e6df32ff7433e9173dd874f15304d28feec"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the architecture. Let me create a backup and develop the 15-analyst version. First, let me create a backup:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h3vt5g1jiedy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local-backup\" 2>$null; Copy-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local\\tradingagents\" -Destination \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local-backup\\\" -Recurse -Force; Copy-Item -Path \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local\\api\\main.py\" -Destination \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace-finance\\TradingAgents-AShare-local-backup\\\" -Force; Write-Host \"Backup completed\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38613,"output":651,"cacheRead":32319,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71583,"cost":{"input":0.0115839,"output":0.0007812,"cacheRead":0.0009695699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013334669999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774105078738}}
