{"type":"message","id":"aadcbba8","parentId":"a471a6a4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:17:40.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have completed the development of the 15-analyst version. Let me now provide a summary of the work done:\n\n## Summary of Work Completed\n\n1. **Created 7 new analyst modules**:\n   - `industry_analyst.py` - Industry trends and competition analysis\n   - `valuation_analyst.py` - DCF, PE ratio, and other valuation methods\n   - `financial_quality_analyst.py` - Profit quality and cash flow quality\n   - `management_analyst.py` - Management team evaluation\n   - `risk_analyst.py` - Risk factor analysis\n   - `institutional_analyst.py` - Institutional holdings analysis\n   - `flows_analyst.py` - Money flow analysis\n\n2. **Updated core files**:\n   - `tradingagents/agents/__init__.py` - Added imports for new analysts\n   - `tradingagents/graph/trading_graph.py` - Added tool nodes for new analysts\n   - `tradingagents/graph/setup.py` - Added setup for new analysts\n   - `api/main.py` - Updated ANALYST_ORDER, ANALYST_AGENT_NAMES, ANALYST_REPORT_MAP, and default selected_analysts\n   - `tradingagents/prompts/zh.py` - Added system prompts for all new analysts\n\n3. **All modified files have been copied to the running Docker container**\n\n4. **The container is running successfully** on port 8000\n\nThe testing couldn't be fully completed because the API token generated in the original container is tied to its database, but the code is syntactically correct and the container starts without errors.","thinkingSignature":"1862123c56ab16d5240c796dbdfdafde394769b742f8a4a475a9a51126a08939"},{"type":"text","text":"## Development Complete - 15 Analyst Version\n\n### Summary of Accomplishments\n\n**Created 7 new analyst modules** (adding to the existing 8):\n1. **industry_analyst.py** - 行业分析师 (Industry trends & competition)\n2. **valuation_analyst.py** - 估值分析师 (DCF, PE, PB valuation)\n3. **financial_quality_analyst.py** - 财务质量分析师 (Profit & cash flow quality)\n4. **management_analyst.py** - 管理层分析师 (Management team evaluation)\n5. **risk_analyst.py** - 风险分析师 (Risk factor analysis)\n6. **institutional_analyst.py** - 机构持仓分析师 (Institutional holdings)\n7. **flows_analyst.py** - 资金流向分析师 (Money flow analysis)\n\n**Total: 15 analysts + game_theory manager**\n\n### Files Modified\n- `tradingagents/agents/__init__.py` - Added new analyst imports\n- `tradingagents/graph/trading_graph.py` - Added tool nodes\n- `tradingagents/graph/setup.py` - Added analyst setup\n- `api/main.py` - Updated analyst configuration\n- `tradingagents/prompts/zh.py` - Added system prompts\n\n### Current Status\n- ✅ All Python files compile without syntax errors\n- ✅ Modified files copied to Docker container\n- ✅ Container running successfully on port 8000\n- ⚠️ Full API testing requires token regeneration (token tied to original database)\n\n### Backup Location\n- Original code backed up to: `TradingAgents-AShare-local-backup/`\n\n### Next Steps for Testing\n1. Generate a new API token in the new container\n2. Run a test analysis with selected_analysts including the new ones\n3. Verify all 15 analysts produce reports\n\nThe development follows the key principles:\n- Only read and studied code before modifying\n- Created files in local workspace first\n- Maintained backward compatibility with existing 6-analyst setup"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64196,"output":756,"cacheRead":32319,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97271,"cost":{"input":0.0192588,"output":0.0009071999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009695699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02113557}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774106244046}}
